## Verification Checklist

- [ ] `cleanupPreview()` function created at `packages/core/src/deploy/preview-cleanup.ts`
- [ ] Container is stopped with 30-second graceful timeout
- [ ] Container is removed after stopping (frees container name)
- [ ] Port is released via `PortAllocator.release()`
- [ ] Caddy route is removed for `pr-{N}--{slug}.{domain}`
- [ ] All preview Docker images for the PR are deleted (`{slug}:pr-{N}-*`)
- [ ] Deployment record status set to `archived`
- [ ] Each cleanup step is wrapped in try/catch (best-effort)
- [ ] Remaining steps execute even if one step fails
- [ ] Function is idempotent (safe to call multiple times)
- [ ] Handles missing resources gracefully (container already stopped, port already released, etc.)
- [ ] Logging at info level for each successful cleanup step
- [ ] Logging at error level for each failed cleanup step
- [ ] Summary log at end indicates success or partial failure

